Description: Sparebanken Vest is a Norway-based independent savings bank. The Bank provides financial services to both the private and corporate sectors. The Bank offers online and mobile banking services, card issue, payment services, mortgage and different kind of small loans, saving and retire account, property and health insurance and real estate credit among others.
